{"product_id":"copy-of-norrskin-face-foam-cleanser-150ml","title":"NorrSkin Face Repair Serum 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eBoosts skin with vitamins and supports skin repairing processes. Balances sebum production \u0026amp; skin tone. Through gentle exfoliation, tightens skin pores.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eBenefits: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVisibly improves skin texture and tone\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBy gentle exfoliation it reduces appearance of skin pores, dark spots and wrinkles \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnti inflammatory, anti acne\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCalms down redness and irritation\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBalances oil\/sebum production with 5% Niacinamide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSupport regenerating and repairing processes in your skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAzelaic Acid\u003c\/span\u003e regulates sebum production, lightens discolouration, reduces excessive keratinisation, gently exfoliates. Has antibacterial properties.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eNiacinamide\u003c\/span\u003e, also knows as Vitamin B3 and strong antioxidant, has a cleaning, detoxifying and brightening properties. Decreases redness and irritations on the skin. Stimulates elasticity.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eLinseed Extract\u003c\/span\u003e is extra-rich, plant-derived source of Omega-3 fatty acids. Provides a nourishing and protective barrier for your skin, enhancing its natural glow.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e91,9% natural origin ingredients, dermatologically tested.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply a small amount of serum on clean skin on your face and neck. Wait until absorbed. Proceed to the Norrskin House of Lin cream.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Propanediol, Glycerin, Azelaic Acid, Niacinamide, Arginine, Sodium Hydroxide, Linum Usitatissimum Seed Extract, Fragaria Vesca Fruit Extract, Panthenol, Pantolactone, Xanthan Gum, Lactic Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Levulinate, Levulinic Acid, Parfum, Trisodium Ethylenediamine Disuccinate, Polysorbate 80, Hexyl Cinnamal. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNatural Certified | Clean Certified | Vegan Certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eInspired by Hälsingland, Sweden.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNorrSkin plants 1 tree for every product sold.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"bioskina","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49308328132935,"sku":null,"price":34.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/norrskin-face-repair-serum-30ml-625618.png?v=1739897346","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/copy-of-norrskin-face-foam-cleanser-150ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}